The consumption pattern of pork on a global capacity indicates an increasing demand for white meat.  In South Africa a production / consumption gap exits in the pork industry. The growing demand and shortage of pork justifies the need to increase local production.  There is scope for export   Pork produced will be of a high quality and will comply to international standards.

The concept is based on a 300 sow unit for a medium to large commercial production facility and can be grown to accommodate a 5000 sow unit.

Feasibility calculations indicate a positive growth in the Gross Margin from year 1 to 10.  Cash flow projections indicate smooth cash inflows and outflows on a yearly basis, making it possible to remunerate funding over a period of ten years, including interest.

This is a realistic, workable proposal and will benefit all involved.

product_desc:

GenWye is developing a smart locker service offers a different approach to delivering parcels in South Africa. It will provide 24/7 access for the customer to send or receive items at a convenient location at a time that suits them

name: AtomCert
product_desc:
When any developer wants to add https (SSL) to their website they are required to register a certificate from a Certificate Authority. This authority verifies and acts as source of truth as to if the domain can be trusted and is published by a specific company that it might claim to be. This makes E-Commerce so safe as it is today. 

This is all fine and well but the problem comes in when developers deal with these certificates. They are often passed around like simple files and send in E-Mails ... This causes many holes that attackers could use to exploit and even get the keys to impersonate a company.

We decided to make this both easier and more secure. The system we are building allows anyone, expert to beginner, to register a certificate. And with these certificates grouped into teams you can control access to them, along with view a audit log of actions performed by whom and when.

We believe this is the future and will make certificates easier and more secure for everyone.
high_concept: Manage and create your SSL certificates efficiently in a UI that won't fight you

Chronica is an opensource project (https://github/evanx/chronic) with effectively zero overhead, and may attract attention as a free entry-level service that rivals Pingdom and New Relic, and obviates the need to install opensource solutions such as Nagios or OSSEC.

The consumer is: 

- Operator of a Linux system, who wants an instant monitoring solution, e.g. without having to install Nagios or OSSEC. 

- Linux admin who wants custom monitoring using shell commands. 

- Operator of a Java application which can be monitored via its log4j logs.

name: VitaCAD
product_desc:
Water Jet Cutting is a computer controlled cutting process by which plain water is pressurised to 60 000 psi (+/- 3500 bar) forced through a jewel orifice and cutting nozzle, resulting in a water stream, moving at +/- 1700 mph. A cutting abrasive is then introduced to the stream, making it possible to cut through materials up to 150mm thick. 
This machines is suitable for cutting all materials, ranging from:
Acrylic, alloys, aluminium, brass, ceramic, composites, copper, felt, foam, fibreglass, glass, granite, laminates, marble, plastics, rubber, silicon, stainless steel, mild steel, titanium, wood, etc.
The most important benefit of water jet cutting is the ability to cut material without interfering with the materials inherent structure, as there is "no heat affected zone". This in turn allows metals to be cut without harming or changing its intrinsic properties, and obtaining an accuracy of 0.2mm

These commercial, fast growing banks focus on financing environmental projects, social entrepreneurship and community businesses that are sorely needed here.Water will connect savers and investors who want to change the world they live in for the better with companies doing just that.  Sustainable Banking.
high_concept: Bank financing enterprises which create social, environmental or cultural value.

name: Bitlr
product_desc: Bitlr.com allows users to upload and share any and all types of files with other users on the site. Only registered users can access content from the site and only users who follow one another can see which files have been uploaded and may download them for free. Users may also create groups to share content and files with all members on the site. These groups are also hidden from the public and can only be accessed via invite. All updates are streamed in real time. Similar to Facebook
high_concept: Bitlr allows you to share files that other websites wont.
status: We are now growing by 80 + members per day :) Not bad for our second month online.

name: TrustFabric
product_desc:
TrustFabric is a Vendor Relationship Management (VRM) platform. Businesses use CRM systems to manage relationships with their customers, while VRM in turn allows customers to manage relationships with businesses.

TrustFabric recognised a need to offer customers a platform to represent their side of the VRM+CRM relationship. TrustFabric makes businesses relationships more efficient while giving customers more control over their personal information.
high_concept: Smarter relationships between businesses and individiduals.
markets: Consumer Internet, Open Source, CRM, Data Security
status: We launched a new video recently: http://www.trustfabric.org/2011/07/15/trustfabric-connect-video/

name: SmartSim Solutions
product_desc: SmartSim Solutions is the exclusive supplier of Bridging Antenna's that help NFC Sim Cards & NFC µSD Cards to perform wireless smart card transactions. Bridging Antenna's can be attached to handset batteries as a sticker (or embedded) to overcome the transmission shielding effect of batteries which typically cover most Sim Card and Micro SD Card slots in the market. Our Antenna Bridge enables networks to quickly and seamlessly retrofit handsets with radio enabled NFC sim Cards or µSD SD Cards.
markets: Mobile Commerce, Mobile Payments, High Tech, NFC

name: Cosapien
product_desc: Cosapien's SaaS helps knowledge workers to collaborate with integrity. You can enjoy productive meetings. And now you can manage collaboration with high quality information.
status: Cosapien now enables live performance management (at zero overhead) ... know how many commitments are overdue (per department/individual).

name: Sasashani
product_desc: Sasashani is a media holding company focused on building a suite of LIVE TV channels that are 100% LIVE (as in real-time). This provides viewers with authenticity, indeterminacy of process and outcome as well as interactivity. Our channels: LIVE wildlife, LIVE celebrity (paparazzi), LIVE medical procedures, LIVE danger (risky situations and activities) and LIVE auctions. The channels are licensed to pay-tv operators globally.
high_concept: LIVE TV, streaming platforms, 3DTV & immersive experiences
markets: Television, Video Streaming, Social Television, World Domination
status: busy developing LIVE extreme sports and LIVE 3D cage fighting broadcasts!!

name: evly

evly enables constructive engagement with your customers, staff and fans by combining crowd collaboration with social networks. everywhere. continuously.

name: StudentGrid

StudentGrid links students to businesses through social networking (online and offline), enabling them to complete tasks in a secure online workspace to make money and gain work experience in their line of study. Information sharing and mentorship is encouraged. Everything happens online and businesses benefit from the lower rates students charge.
www.seplatform.com
